## How to Attribute This Work

When using or citing this framework, please provide attribution as follows:

**For Academic Citations:**

APA Style:
```
Choudhary, A. D. (2026). Draft regulatory framework for mandatory disclosure and 
oversight of AI-generated and AI-altered video content. Student Global Summit. 
https://github.com/yourusername/ai-policy-framework
```

MLA Style:
```
Choudhary, Aditya Devraj. "Draft Regulatory Framework for Mandatory Disclosure 
and Oversight of AI-Generated and AI-Altered Video Content." Student Global 
Summit, Feb. 2026, github.com/yourusername/ai-policy-framework.
```

**For Policy Documents or Reports:**
```
This framework incorporates provisions from the "Draft Regulatory Framework for 
Mandatory Disclosure and Oversight of AI-Generated and AI-Altered Video Content" 
by Aditya Devraj Choudhary (Student Global Summit, 2026), available at 
[repository URL], licensed under CC BY 4.0.
```

**For Derivative Works:**
```
This [policy/document/framework] is adapted from work by Aditya Devraj Choudhary 
for the Student Global Summit, licensed under CC BY 4.0.
```

